{"tid":533932,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"概率問題","createTime":"2018-01-19T10:08:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-19T17:14:01.000Z","uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c8bac1ce899970ac0e5747c1140faa9b27c06672","tid":533932,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:08:33.000Z","msg":"假設買大細 圍骰唔係通殺<br />\nA有$20，$10 1注，最多係贏$10或者輸哂$20就唔玩<br />\n咁A贏嘅概率就會係（0.5)+(0.5^3+0.5^5+0.5^7+...) 有錯請指出<br />\n<br />\n咁如果<br />\n(1) A有$20，$5 1注，同樣最多係贏$10或者輸哂$20就唔玩<br />\n每個stage贏嘅概率係幾多 （e.g 我已經輸左$5，要贏返去到$10機率係幾多）<br />\n<br />\n（2） A有$20，$1 1注，同樣最多係贏$10或者輸哂$20就唔玩<br />\n每個stage贏嘅概率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n（3）A有$40，$10 手注，最多係贏$10或者輸哂$20就唔玩<br />\n每個stage贏嘅概率係幾多<br />\n<br />\n條數搞左我好耐都計少左啲case, 跪求連登仔指教"},{"pid":"21e4d38c83aa2a38ad198e11a5d0ba5a14121b81","tid":533932,"uid":41887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:19:48.000Z","msg":"markov chain<br />\n好似係"},{"pid":"07980b0d2c47343728c44422c3226f79b2d29eab","tid":533932,"uid":29408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>markov chain<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\nMonte Carlo Markov Chain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2717d56009c4a32efe79e259c8dc103ccf2b9ef0","tid":533932,"uid":69174,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07980b0d2c47343728c44422c3226f79b2d29eab","tid":533932,"uid":29408,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T10:21:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>markov chain<br />\n好似係</blockquote><br />\nMonte Carlo Markov Chain<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-19T17:14:01.000Z","msg":"冇冇例題可以講下點計？<br />\n或者用上面1條做例子<br />\n聽fd講用matrix會計到🤩"}]}